Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.15,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Eles não poderão acordar desse sonho
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.16,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Me pergunto porque eu olho para a torre
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.12,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Durante toda a noite, ao luar, você janta
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.42,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Minhas mãos seguram tudo neste mundo
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.34,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Eu tenho, tenho tudo em meus ossos
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.17,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Estou tentando começar essa rotina
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.26,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Não há luz nesta noite sagrada
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.43,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Por que não tenho o que tanto desejo?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.01,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Não posso deixar de sair
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.35,0:03:18.10,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Glória e fortuna
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.23,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Um futuro perdido no topo da cidadela
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.11,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Até mesmo a esperança será esmagada
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.53,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Como um cadáver
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.90,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Continue matando mais e mais
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.90,0:03:34.53,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Vamos jogar os dados e dançar
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.87,0:03:40.79,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Deixe os pesadelos nos enlouquecer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.83,0:03:46.67,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Vamos dançar pela última vez
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.88,0:03:51.59,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Mesmo que o vazio nos consuma
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.47,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Eles não poderão acordar desse sonho
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.27,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Matem-me, rápido, rápido
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.48,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}A escuridão é infinita
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.11,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Não pode ser derramado
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.94,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Estou caindo
